00:29:24,896 --> 00:29:25,831
Yeah.

268
00:29:26,098 --> 00:29:29,368
That woman is up to no good
from the start.

269
00:29:29,968 --> 00:29:33,071
She assigns overtime work
to our daughter every night,

270
00:29:33,138 --> 00:29:35,841
but she only gives her a low salary.

271
00:29:36,174 --> 00:29:37,609
Well... No.

272
00:29:37,676 --> 00:29:39,478
Money is not the most important problem.

273
00:29:39,544 --> 00:29:42,347
The most important thing is, Shancai comes
home so late every day because of her.

274
00:29:42,414 --> 00:29:45,050
She wants me to starve to death.

275
00:29:45,550 --> 00:29:49,788
So I'll never let her scheme succeed.

276
00:29:52,157 --> 00:29:54,459
-Stop eating.
-Oh, you...

277
00:29:54,993 --> 00:29:58,163
-Oh, you...
-Fine. I won't eat.

278
00:30:01,133 --> 00:30:04,269
-Mom, I'm home.
-Shancai, you're back.

279
00:30:05,304 --> 00:30:06,571
It smells so good.

280
00:30:07,039 --> 00:30:09,374
Grab some food to restore your strength.

281
00:30:09,441 --> 00:30:13,312
So that you'll have the power
to fight that evil woman.

282
00:30:13,378 --> 00:30:14,713
Who is that evil woman?

283
00:30:15,147 --> 00:30:17,683
Who else could she be?
Of course, I mean that Daoming Feng.

284
00:30:18,450 --> 00:30:19,318
Fine.

285
00:30:23,588 --> 00:30:25,090
Dad, why are you staring at them?

286
00:30:25,157 --> 00:30:26,091
Let's eat.

287
00:30:26,158 --> 00:30:27,159
That's right.

288
00:30:27,225 --> 00:30:30,295
You could've said it earlier.
I've waited for it for so long.

289
00:30:30,362 --> 00:30:32,264
Why did you come home so late?
Come on. Take a seat.

290
00:30:32,331 --> 00:30:34,599
-Let's eat. Come on.
-All right. I'll put my bag away first.

291
00:30:34,666 --> 00:30:36,234
Okay. Hurry up.

292
00:30:37,602 --> 00:30:40,305
Hey. Eat slowly, will you?

293
00:30:42,474 --> 00:30:43,575
There are vegetables here.

294
00:30:44,009 --> 00:30:45,377
-Mom, this is for you.
-Okay.

295
00:30:51,516 --> 00:30:53,852
I feel so happy that our whole family
can eat dinner together.

296
00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:56,288
-Dad.
-Yeah?

297
00:30:56,355 --> 00:30:58,657
There won't be any problem
about the car delivery tomorrow, right?

298
00:31:00,258 --> 00:31:01,293
Honey.

299
00:31:01,927 --> 00:31:04,363
Your veggie egg porridge is perfect.

300
00:31:04,896 --> 00:31:07,199
It's so amazing
that I can never have enough of it.

301
00:31:07,666 --> 00:31:10,802
It's all thanks to your sales performance
for this month.

302
00:31:10,869 --> 00:31:13,271
Otherwise, we might not be able
to afford congee.

303
00:31:19,378 --> 00:31:24,082
Shancai, you should introduce your dad
to more rich guys.

304
00:31:24,149 --> 00:31:26,518
No. I mean, good friends.

305
00:31:26,585 --> 00:31:28,453
No matter who they are,

306
00:31:28,520 --> 00:31:30,455
as long as your dad is selling cars,

307
00:31:30,522 --> 00:31:32,924
our sales performance will be improved.

308
00:31:32,991 --> 00:31:34,826
-Just like the last time,
-Yeah, right.

309
00:31:34,893 --> 00:31:36,762
that Master Huaze Lei.

310
00:31:37,329 --> 00:31:39,064
He is our lifesaver.

311
00:31:39,131 --> 00:31:41,032
-Thanks, Mom.
-Right? Hey.

312
00:31:42,968 --> 00:31:44,169
Got rice on my face?

313
00:31:45,003 --> 00:31:45,971
Just wipe it off.

314
00:31:46,037 --> 00:31:49,875
Shancai, who is the one
ordering the van from us?

315
00:31:50,208 --> 00:31:51,743
It must be Master Qinghe, right?

316
00:31:52,744 --> 00:31:53,712
No.

317
00:31:54,913 --> 00:31:58,750
Then it must be
your new aristocratic friend, right?

318
00:31:59,985 --> 00:32:01,520
Actually, it's Daoming Si.

319
00:32:09,828 --> 00:32:12,063
He...

320
00:32:12,130 --> 00:32:13,765
Has he regained his memory?

321
00:32:14,499 --> 00:32:15,634
That's great.

322
00:32:16,168 --> 00:32:19,104
Your relationship with Daoming Si,

323
00:32:19,738 --> 00:32:22,374
hey, is just like
this veggie egg porridge.

324
00:32:23,909 --> 00:32:26,978
It's so thick that no one can break it.

325
00:32:27,045 --> 00:32:28,547
You're inseparable.

326
00:32:29,181 --> 00:32:31,683
Dad, stop writing your cheesy script.

327
00:32:32,083 --> 00:32:33,718
Daoming Si hasn't regained his memory.

328
00:32:33,785 --> 00:32:35,720
He ordered that van for Yesha.

329
00:32:37,322 --> 00:32:38,290
Yesha?

330
00:32:38,924 --> 00:32:41,827
You mean that weird princess?

331
00:32:43,295 --> 00:32:44,196
Shancai.

332
00:32:46,531 --> 00:32:48,800
Things between Daoming Si and me
are not what you're thinking.

333
00:32:49,267 --> 00:32:52,270
All I can say is that we're friends now.

334
00:32:53,338 --> 00:32:54,940
Maybe it's hard for you to imagine,

335
00:32:55,006 --> 00:32:58,009
but this is the most suitable word
to describe our relationship now.

336
00:32:58,910 --> 00:33:02,180
At least he won't reject
my concern for him.

337
00:33:03,648 --> 00:33:05,884
This is very important to me.

338
00:33:05,951 --> 00:33:07,786
Really very important.

339
00:33:13,492 --> 00:33:15,227
Why are you looking at me like that?

340
00:33:23,835 --> 00:33:24,703
Hello.

341
00:33:25,270 --> 00:33:26,338
Daoming Si.

342
00:33:27,639 --> 00:33:30,308
Tomorrow morning at nine o'clock,
you can go talk to my dad.

343
00:33:31,376 --> 00:33:32,277
You're welcome.

344
00:33:36,348 --> 00:33:39,417
Dad, tomorrow morning at nine o'clock,
Daoming Si will be there to take the van.

345
00:33:40,852 --> 00:33:42,320
No problem. I know.

346
00:33:43,255 --> 00:33:44,322
Let's eat.

347
00:33:45,557 --> 00:33:47,292
<i>In the story of Daoming Si,</i>

348
00:33:47,359 --> 00:33:49,327
<i>I've turned from the protagonist
into a supporting role.</i>

349
00:33:49,661 --> 00:33:51,796
<i>Everyone thinks that I'm stupid,</i>

350
00:33:51,863 --> 00:33:53,198
<i>that I'm crazy.</i>

351
00:33:53,832 --> 00:33:55,433
<i>This is how things are.</i>

352
00:33:55,500 --> 00:33:57,869
<i>I can't step out
of the Daoming Si's story.</i>

353
00:33:59,070 --> 00:34:00,805
<i>There's no way out.</i>

354
00:34:17,756 --> 00:34:18,757
Guess who I am.

355
00:34:20,392 --> 00:34:21,326
What?

356
00:34:22,627 --> 00:34:23,962
Are you thinking about something?

357
00:34:24,262 --> 00:34:25,163
No.

358
00:34:26,998 --> 00:34:28,600
Let me tell you something.

359
00:34:28,667 --> 00:34:30,635
It's bad news. Don't get upset.

360
00:34:31,369 --> 00:34:32,437
What is it?

361
00:34:33,605 --> 00:34:35,140
Promise me first that you won't get upset.

362
00:34:35,206 --> 00:34:36,675
Just tell me already.

363
00:34:39,311 --> 00:34:41,146
The breakfast van is ready.

364
00:34:42,314 --> 00:34:43,848
-Really? Are you sure?
-Yes.

365
00:34:43,915 --> 00:34:45,517
-Yeah.
-How did you know that?

366
00:34:45,584 --> 00:34:46,551
I just saw it.

367
00:34:46,618 --> 00:34:48,453
-Really? You saw it.
-Yeah.

368
00:34:48,720 --> 00:34:50,121
Or did they just tell you that?

369
00:34:50,555 --> 00:34:51,790
What do you think?

370
00:35:02,634 --> 00:35:04,235
Why is your score so low?

371
00:35:04,636 --> 00:35:05,704
You suck.

372
00:35:08,206 --> 00:35:09,207
Okay, one more round.

373
00:35:10,041 --> 00:35:11,076
I'll defeat you.

374
00:35:12,711 --> 00:35:14,980
You've told me that ten times today.

375
00:35:17,115 --> 00:35:18,450
You look down on me, huh?

376
00:35:19,884 --> 00:35:21,586
Maybe I can't beat you in some things,

377
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:23,722
but today, I'm going to win.

378
00:35:25,757 --> 00:35:27,726
Yeah, you're the best.

379
00:35:30,829 --> 00:35:33,298
Your mind is somewhere else.
What happened?

380
00:35:39,504 --> 00:35:40,839
Whose mind is somewhere else?

381
00:35:43,775 --> 00:35:45,543
Just go if you have things to do.

382
00:35:45,610 --> 00:35:47,278
I'm going to be out of the hospital today.

383
00:35:48,780 --> 00:35:50,315
Didn't you say that I got nothing to do?

384
00:35:53,852 --> 00:35:54,819
Give me a moment.

385
00:35:56,221 --> 00:35:57,122
Hello.

386
00:36:03,228 --> 00:36:05,463
Didn't I tell you I'm with Ximen
at the hospital?

387
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:09,668
This is not an excuse.

388
00:36:09,734 --> 00:36:11,136
This is a reason.

389
00:36:14,406 --> 00:36:16,341
Fine. I'll pick her up.

390
00:36:33,658 --> 00:36:34,959
Still on your blind date tour?

391
00:36:37,295 --> 00:36:39,764
Are you dumping her
because she's too ugly?

392
00:36:43,001 --> 00:36:44,069
It's not like that.

393
00:36:46,871 --> 00:36:49,007
So maybe she's too hot
and out of your league?

394
00:36:50,208 --> 00:36:52,711
Nonsense. I, Meizuo--

395
00:36:52,777 --> 00:36:54,145
Then go get her.

396
00:36:54,512 --> 00:36:55,680
What are you doing here?

397
00:36:58,516 --> 00:37:00,418
It's because you're going
to be discharged today.

398
00:37:00,485 --> 00:37:01,653
I'll take you home.

399
00:37:01,953 --> 00:37:03,154
Oh, come on.

400
00:37:03,221 --> 00:37:05,256
My mom and dad will pick me up
after I get discharged.

401
00:37:05,957 --> 00:37:09,060
It's because you like her so much.
You're acting like you don't like her.

402
00:37:09,794 --> 00:37:11,763
Who's acting?

403
00:37:11,996 --> 00:37:13,665
It hurts! I'm a patient!

404
00:37:18,369 --> 00:37:19,537
Fine.

405
00:37:21,473 --> 00:37:22,607
I'll go get her.

406
00:37:24,642 --> 00:37:27,178
I'll let her know that I'm not a guy
she can handle.

407
00:37:32,784 --> 00:37:34,652
What a friend you are! It hurts!

408
00:37:35,653 --> 00:37:36,788
Okay. I'm sorry.

409
00:37:37,122 --> 00:37:38,089
Soda.

410
00:37:39,524 --> 00:37:40,792
Good boy.

411
00:37:41,826 --> 00:37:42,761
I'm leaving now.

412
00:37:43,995 --> 00:37:45,263
-Drive safe.
-Okay.

413
00:37:59,778 --> 00:38:00,912
Why are we here again?

414
00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:04,616
Shopping must be a hobby
for ladies like you.

415
00:38:05,150 --> 00:38:07,685
I have no interest in shopping
with a lady.

416
00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:10,955
I apologize for our last date.
I should've paid your bill.

417
00:38:11,623 --> 00:38:13,758
Everything you are going to buy today
is on me.

418
00:38:27,605 --> 00:38:28,673
You don't need to pick me up.

419
00:38:35,046 --> 00:38:36,047
I don't need to?

420
00:38:46,991 --> 00:38:47,859
Be careful.

421
00:38:48,326 --> 00:38:51,696
Mom, I'm fine now.
Don't treat me like a patient.

422
00:38:52,197 --> 00:38:53,998
The doctors only allowed you
to leave the hospital.

423
00:38:54,065 --> 00:38:56,501
They didn't say
that your body is fully recovered.

424
00:38:58,903 --> 00:39:00,138
I know.

425
00:39:00,471 --> 00:39:02,974
That's why I didn't go to the company,
instead I went home with you.

426
00:39:03,041 --> 00:39:04,542
Don't think about your company for now.

427
00:39:04,809 --> 00:39:07,812
I tell you what. You have to rest at home
for at least one week.

428
00:39:08,813 --> 00:39:10,048
Three days.

429
00:39:10,381 --> 00:39:11,416
Five days.

430
00:39:12,317 --> 00:39:13,418
Four days, okay?

431
00:39:13,484 --> 00:39:15,086
Five days, that's a deal.

432
00:39:15,153 --> 00:39:16,821
I'm not doing business with you.

433
00:39:18,857 --> 00:39:20,625
Ma'am, your husband is back.

434
00:39:21,759 --> 00:39:23,228
I just went to the hospital.

435
00:39:23,294 --> 00:39:25,029
The nurse said you had already gone home.

436
00:39:25,663 --> 00:39:28,533
I thought you were busy
so I didn't call you.

437
00:39:32,537 --> 00:39:34,005
Let me help you set your things up.

438
00:39:34,072 --> 00:39:35,506
You should chat with your dad, okay?

439
00:39:39,444 --> 00:39:40,812
Our son just came home.

440
00:39:41,646 --> 00:39:44,215
How about we have dinner together tonight?

441
00:39:46,150 --> 00:39:47,285
Right, Mom.

442
00:39:47,352 --> 00:39:49,687
It's a chance to help me recover, right?

443
00:39:51,756 --> 00:39:52,957
What would you like to eat?

444
00:39:53,825 --> 00:39:55,360
Spicy wontons, of course.

445
00:39:55,426 --> 00:39:56,961
You can't eat spicy food now.

446
00:39:58,429 --> 00:40:00,431
Then they are just wontons, right?

447
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:04,903
You just can't eat spicy food now, okay?

448
00:40:18,182 --> 00:40:19,250
Mom, what's the matter?

449
00:40:19,317 --> 00:40:21,319
<i>Did you send Xiaociao's friend home?</i>

450
00:40:22,186 --> 00:40:23,021
What?

451
00:40:23,087 --> 00:40:25,723
<i>I didn't know
that my son is so thoughtful.</i>

452
00:40:25,790 --> 00:40:27,725
<i>I loved that dress.</i>

453
00:40:29,427 --> 00:40:30,628
What are you talking about?

454
00:40:30,895 --> 00:40:32,397
<i>Don't be shy.</i>

455
00:40:32,664 --> 00:40:34,832
<i>Xiaociao brought the gifts home.</i>

456
00:40:34,899 --> 00:40:36,701
<i>You're so dumb.</i>

457
00:40:36,768 --> 00:40:40,438
<i>Why didn't you send Xiaociao back first
before you sent her friend home?</i>

458
00:40:40,772 --> 00:40:43,041
<i>Xiaociao brought a lot of stuff
by herself.</i>

459
00:40:44,409 --> 00:40:46,644
<i>You don't know how to take care of others,
just like your dad.</i>

460
00:40:47,979 --> 00:40:50,248
<i>Okay, I just want to tell you--</i>

461
00:40:50,315 --> 00:40:52,817
-Mom, that--
-<i>I'm very happy now, it's okay.</i>

462
00:41:16,741 --> 00:41:17,742
Xiaociao...

463
00:41:41,699 --> 00:41:42,767
What do you want?

464
00:41:44,902 --> 00:41:45,937
What do you mean?

465
00:41:47,572 --> 00:41:49,607
I mean, do you have any idea
what you're doing?

466
00:41:49,874 --> 00:41:52,744
My mom and your mom
are planning our future for us.

467
00:41:52,810 --> 00:41:53,811
Don't you know that?

468
00:41:54,946 --> 00:41:55,913
Yes, I know.

469
00:41:56,280 --> 00:41:58,182
That's why I'm dating you.

470
00:41:59,751 --> 00:42:01,586
You mean, you accept
what they planned for you?

471
00:42:02,987 --> 00:42:06,124
Do you like being their puppet,
doing whatever they tell you to do?

472
00:42:07,392 --> 00:42:10,762
You're right that my parents
have encouraged me to date you.

473
00:42:11,262 --> 00:42:16,000
But considering our family backgrounds
and education,

474
00:42:16,067 --> 00:42:17,635
we are perfect for each other.

475
00:42:18,369 --> 00:42:19,804
Why can't you be like me?

476
00:42:19,871 --> 00:42:22,507
Calm down
and try to be in a relationship with me.

477
00:42:23,307 --> 00:42:24,509
After all, you're a man.

478
00:42:24,575 --> 00:42:26,677
You won't lose anything,
no matter how this turns out.

479
00:42:27,311 --> 00:42:28,980
But we don't have feelings for each other.

480
00:42:31,315 --> 00:42:32,583
Feelings can be developed.

481
00:42:33,051 --> 00:42:35,353
And you don't know me at all.

482
00:42:36,087 --> 00:42:37,555
You don't know me, either.

483
00:42:38,589 --> 00:42:40,658
But at least I know you're a good man.

484
00:42:45,730 --> 00:42:49,100
Okay, I'll show you how good I am.

485
00:43:50,795 --> 00:43:51,696
Come on.

486
00:43:52,597 --> 00:43:53,431
Tired, right?

487
00:43:54,799 --> 00:43:55,633
Cheers.

488
00:43:55,700 --> 00:43:57,301
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

489
00:44:01,539 --> 00:44:02,807
Meizuo.

490
00:44:03,141 --> 00:44:04,575
Don't you want to introduce us?

491
00:44:11,516 --> 00:44:13,584
Hi, nice to meet you.

492
00:44:13,818 --> 00:44:15,853
I'm Xiaociao, girlfriend of Meizuo.

493
00:44:16,487 --> 00:44:17,488
Girlfriend?

494
00:44:18,623 --> 00:44:19,757
What a coincidence.

495
00:44:20,458 --> 00:44:22,727
I'm Meizuo's girlfriend number 8.

496
00:44:23,161 --> 00:44:25,696
She's number 20.

497
00:44:26,531 --> 00:44:27,565
What about you?

498
00:44:28,032 --> 00:44:29,567
What's your number?

499
00:44:35,706 --> 00:44:37,241
I don't know what my number is.

500
00:44:38,509 --> 00:44:41,379
But I'm sure that I'm the last one.

501
00:44:43,881 --> 00:44:48,152
I think you don't really know Meizuo.

502
00:44:49,420 --> 00:44:52,223
Since you know Meizuo very well,

503
00:44:52,290 --> 00:44:55,493
can I consult you about Meizuo
from now on?

504
00:44:56,294 --> 00:44:58,095
You want to consult us?

505
00:44:58,896 --> 00:45:05,836
But Meizuo still surprises us
in different ways every now and then.

506
00:45:06,837 --> 00:45:10,474
What part do you want to consult with us?

507
00:45:11,342 --> 00:45:14,078
The best parts, of course.

508
00:45:15,179 --> 00:45:18,583
But I'm afraid
that you can't learn them well.

509
00:45:19,183 --> 00:45:22,486
There's nothing I haven't learned well
since my childhood.

510
00:45:23,921 --> 00:45:27,124
Especially your so-called best parts.

511
00:45:32,563 --> 00:45:35,366
Can you learn something like this well?

512
00:46:14,739 --> 00:46:16,941
Hurry up, Daoming Si
has regained his memory!

513
00:47:24,575 --> 00:47:26,577
Subtitle translation by Logan Zhao
